{"tid":1349226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗恐襲相關制裁：凍結財產、禁止籌集財產，和禁止團體招募","createTime":"2019-07-22T09:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T18:57:32.000Z","uid":36592,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d8311eba06f3dad02d1e28d72b54ec665e6cb1","tid":1349226,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"梁啟智：講清楚：是「元朗恐襲」，不是「衝突」<br />\n<br />\n暴力，有好多種。打人，同打爛塊玻璃，就係兩種。而世上無論任何派別都不應該接受的暴力，是以製造恐慌為目的，針對平民百姓的無差別襲擊，簡稱「恐怖襲擊」。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府亂來，612就叫「暴動」，721就叫「衝突」。不，昨晚在元朗發生的是有組織有預謀、持續發生、針對平民百姓並以製造恐慌為目的的無差別襲擊。它就是恐襲。我們要一齊清楚講明，昨晚在元朗發生的是一場恐襲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港法例第575章《聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)條例》規定，「作出或恐嚇作出行動」，懷有「危害作出該行動的人以外的人的生命」的意圖，就是恐怖主義行為。昨晚現場施害者所說的「唔係白衫就打」，完全符合這個定義。所以，說這些人是暴徒還是過輕了。他們是恐怖分子。<br />\n<br />\n既然是恐怖分子，相關的制裁也就適用，包括凍結財產、禁止籌集財產，和禁止團體招募。銀行不可以向他們提供服務，相關的財產亦應被扣留和充公，例如昨晚曾用作庇護恐怖分子的處所。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這些，對於一個正常的政府，都是立即就要做的事。如果不做，接下來的問題就是：香港政府是否正在支持恐怖主義(State Sponsored Terrorism)？林鄭是否準備好國際社會就此制裁香港政府？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AC%9B%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E6%98%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AC%259B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25A5%259A-%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKoD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=8cb6b0b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AC%259B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25A5%259A-%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%2F&h=ae5e3689\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AC%9B%E6%B8%85%E6%A5%9A-%E6%98%AF-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2-%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81/</a>"},{"pid":"7cd9b6e2b43421ff706846697969da1e5658a3e8","tid":1349226,"uid":264314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d7d7f505cf34fb6eaa72b6966c28cf0e7fb208b","tid":1349226,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為721中聯辦、上環抗爭正名：光復香港，時代革命<br />\n撤回送中、收回定性、釋放義士、 追究黑警、還我普選</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e53cfa6f91a05c8a057d34b1e6f3db4dbac35f52","tid":1349226,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為721中聯辦、上環抗爭正名：光復香港，時代革命<br />\n撤回送中、收回定性、釋放義士、 追究黑警、還我普選</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5486841ce06488ddb71bf8439de6038618ecdf32","tid":1349226,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:15:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68f3deb67cef277c1cb6f69fb0a7f02a93e2137a","tid":1349226,"uid":2736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdf2a989df48805c9eae576392206fba6b4255c8","tid":1349226,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b9fd7d21b9d7560ca206fa90e4c1702913b855","tid":1349226,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75f067a55813a4167a5800d93df114a9ad0a4a52","tid":1349226,"uid":276144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:35:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"93497224d355f65477ae4783fb28b37c32517e41","tid":1349226,"uid":19548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:40:14.000Z","msg":"推呀！屌你地老母！"},{"pid":"8acc7ed021e42bd71b226ff1cf8db2cf3